Vanguard Technologies InternationalInc said it was awarded a 2.2 mln dlr contract from the Officeof the Secretary of Defense to provide facilities managementservices.    Under the one-year contract, which also has two one-yearoptional performance periods, the company said it will providelocal area network operations, coordination of hardwareinstallation and maintenance, user support services and systemsand applications programming. Reuter&#3;